data.description: Brand New on the Market.. This cute farmhouse features high ceilings, tons of natural light, and is situated on a 3/4 acre corner lot. The fridge, stove, washer and dryer convey to new owner, a great storage shed w/loft, another spacious building that functions as your laundry room and additional storage, all conveniently located on Hwy 190 East and located in Flood Zone X, no need for flood insurance here! The current configuration has 1 bedroom, but would be easy to enclose the back room to create that 2nd bedroom if needed.. the same for your living & dining areas.. lots of options, let's see what works best for your situation! A great feature is the covered front and back porches that expand your living space! Call to schedule your showing today!
